:"2020-11-17T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"警犬<span class=\"red\"><strong>徐岸暘</strong></span>、水炮車麥鈺熒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"殺人兇手"},{"pid":"7327a7160ecb1eddc4a092d7d51527d9b4b83c9b","tid":2289090,"uid":117282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ed2a742a47987b0c5e4c3bd72126098ece17b7","tid":2289090,"uid":137209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a3bf33cf172a560669fd92883247d8531ae593d","tid":2289090,"uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16ad2d45e1164428e952a869b3fb970e8fdbe6fc","tid":2289090,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:51:06.000Z","msg":"終於提醒人當時有對狗男女結婚 黑警趁人少時狂出TG <br />\n<br />\n果對狗男女仲有人記得嗎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"警犬<span class=\"red\"><strong>徐岸暘</strong></span>、水炮車麥鈺熒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"推一推先 生仔冇屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b111c57cd780c1478692109926cb967d539a0d","tid":2289090,"uid":139388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"入區戒備因「當日有同事結婚，佢哋驚有人搞事<br />\n<br />\n結個婚驚成咁要搵伙計保護<br />\n咁驚就唔好咁大場SHOW囉<br />\n又要威又要帶頭盔"},{"pid":"afda46793ab1cb613e894d07467cd4d8e46496f0","tid":2289090,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}